title: CURTIS CREEK SCHOOL DISTRICT is accepting apps for Food
text:
CURTIS CREEK SCHOOL DISTRICT is accepting apps for Food ad date: 10/13/2015 
CURTIS CREEK SCHOOL DISTRICT is accepting apps for Food Service Assist. 2 hrs/day, 5 days/week, 180 days/year, salary: $12.66 - 17.25/hour. Valid ServSafe Cert. & food service experience preferred. Applications are available at 18755 Standard Road. Apply by 10/21/15, 3:00pm.
